=============================
=  README for ex2: conditions  =
=============================


==================
=  Description:  =
==================

A program that do:

1) Convert one measurement to another
2) Do simple mathematical manipulations
3) Returns the largest and smallest of three numbers
4) Gives the answer of the root equation by user input
5) Gives the area for a given shape base on user input
6) Calculate the BMI and return if it's in the health range or not



